          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The telescope data allowed to extract",
                "break-up cross sections for channels with Li and He",
                "emission. These ions have been identified by their",
                "characteristic energy losses in the thick detectors",
                "numbers 3 and 4 and the detector number 2 served as",
                "target. The following cross sections have been",
                "determined and they correspond to a mean energy for",
                "B-8 of 35.23 MeV/nucl.-",
                "Be-7=2-He-3+2-He-4, Be-7=3-LI-6+1-H-1,",
                "B-8=2-HE-3+A+P,  B-8=3-LI-6+P+P"
              ]
            }
          ],
